  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The second installment in the series—now bigger and better than ever!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each minigame lasts around 2–3 minutes. Packed with fast-paced competitive and cooperative challenges that anyone can enjoy with intuitive controls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports local multiplayer and co-op, plus Remote Play Together. Jump in and have instant fun—even with friends far away!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Free Mode]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788460/extras/aaf5ada03e1ab2bc8e9056a57d838c13.poster.avif?t=1773041611\" width=1170 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788460/extras/aaf5ada03e1ab2bc8e9056a57d838c13.webm?t=1773041611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788460/extras/aaf5ada03e1ab2bc8e9056a57d838c13.mp4?t=1773041611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick your favorite game and play right away!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy an additional selection of co-op games where you must work together to succeed!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Party Mode]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose games to play in succession and compete to be the Party Champion! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design your own characters and invite them to the party to play along! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Character Edit]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788460/extras/f9cfdfe5fb08b59567c44deef6e5fe7f.poster.avif?t=1773041611\" width=1170 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788460/extras/f9cfdfe5fb08b59567c44deef6e5fe7f.webm?t=1773041611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788460/extras/f9cfdfe5fb08b59567c44deef6e5fe7f.mp4?t=1773041611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your ideal hero and bring your unique flair to the party!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>To receive news and update notifications</strong><br>Please click on <strong>Developer: SAT-BOX</strong> at the top of the store page and <strong>Follow</strong> us!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The second installment in the series—now bigger and better than ever!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each minigame lasts around 2–3 minutes. Packed with fast-paced competitive and cooperative challenges that anyone can enjoy with intuitive controls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports local multiplayer and co-op, plus Remote Play Together. Jump in and have instant fun—even with friends far away!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Free Mode]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788460/extras/aaf5ada03e1ab2bc8e9056a57d838c13.poster.avif?t=1773041611\" width=1170 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788460/extras/aaf5ada03e1ab2bc8e9056a57d838c13.webm?t=1773041611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788460/extras/aaf5ada03e1ab2bc8e9056a57d838c13.mp4?t=1773041611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick your favorite game and play right away!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy an additional selection of co-op games where you must work together to succeed!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Party Mode]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose games to play in succession and compete to be the Party Champion! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design your own characters and invite them to the party to play along! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Character Edit]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788460/extras/f9cfdfe5fb08b59567c44deef6e5fe7f.poster.avif?t=1773041611\" width=1170 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared